channel.description:
[IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/63yn9h.png[/img]
Well Its here, Base version of Fubergen's previous versions. This is good for beginners or Coders that want make their client from simple base. NOTE: This Client hasn't Updater already setted to any ftp server.
Includes:
* - Skillcapes * - New loading and connection lost bar * - Jframe with menu * - Music in client (u can put your favorite music) * - Nonrenamed with 377 cache * - Fixed Prayer bug (freezed client, not enough) * - Port and ip Changer in menu * - Screenshot button * - 8 lines chatbox * - Vengeance works * - More options for themes from client's icon * - new hp bar * - Chat filter * - Reshape minimap [Square] * - Edited sprites * - Music in client * - Custom crowns * - Scrollbar fixed * - Renamed Gui * - 3rd armours * - All God's swords * - Almost same features than PF v3's[/COLOR]
[IMG]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/3663/kuvaonhianowz2.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/etifpk.png[/img]
[CENTER] [B]Download link[/B] http://www.fubergen.com/u.php?41
Credits: Sir roju, Fubergen, Pennzoil,Ricscape client v8.5's factors Java got me Stoned for sprites and New chatbox frame Java for themes razvanx - New chatbox buttons(click areas + writing)
The music in client already: Mashlin - The shore
[/CENTER]
